cast.original_title: The Last Letter from Your Lover
cast.overview: A young journalist in London becomes obsessed with a series of letters she discovers that recounts an intense star-crossed love affair from the 1960s.
cast.title: The Last Letter from Your Lover

details.biography: Jasmine Raymond is a British actress born and raised in London. Whilst still training at ArtsEd she filmed in her first feature 'Pinky'. Since graduating in 2019 she landed her first TV debut in the great comedy 'Ted Lasso', which aired August 2020. The Time's newspaper also singled her out for her performance in Greenwich's Theatre online adaption of 'The Secret Life of Ophelia' aired August 2020.
details.name: Jasmine Raymond
